<plot>Something is different about tonight's tabletop game of role-playing fantasy. When Ray is mysteriously injured during an in-game battle, he begins to suspect that a dangerous link to a magical object in the game world is at fault. But, when the other gamers don't believe his theory, Ray must decide: quit playing and risk losing his friends, or continue and risk losing his life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?559736</url></doc>
